        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses effects of natural selection. Discusses absence of blending between geographical races as a problem. Discusses effect of natural selection on productivity of an organism.</p> 
<p>Comments on GJR’s review of Grant Allen’s book [<hi rend="italic">Physiological aesthetics</hi> (1877)].</p> 
